{"tid":543813,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鼓起勇氣問咗個女仔攞電話(長文)","createTime":"2018-01-29T01:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T04:43:58.000Z","uid":122781,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ae043d1e3b312fc338b792c0ed4ec0807f9090","tid":543813,"uid":122781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的 平時返工搭車都會見到個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時見到都會望下佢 佢又會望下我有啲眼神交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住我黎緊個返工時間會唔同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該唔會再見到佢 所以由上星期五開始我想問佢攞電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但星期五個日唔係同一班車 於是我係佢平時落車個站等佢 但過左1班又1班都唔見佢 可能佢返早咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我都無再等 之後星期六(<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我同佢星期六都要返工 真奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )又唔係同一班車 跟住又係落車個站等佢 點知又係過左一班又一班車都唔見 可能佢今日唔使做奴隸呢 於是我又走左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到今日我特登早啲起身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下佢會唔會搭早一班車走咗 搭早個班車都唔見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我又係佢落車個站到等佢 今次見到佢喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住行咗陣段路 我知佢行緊係我附近 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我鼓起勇氣問佢攞電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係被佢拒絕咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒撚真係最忌有自信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好意思騷擾到你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你放心啦過多2日你就唔會再見到我啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢2日返工都係早啲起身避開佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec28f81ac09bee449922e6f56dd4e9478d0f502","tid":543813,"uid":113773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T01:46:09.